CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 12, 1954, pg. 4, reads: "Pitt Graduation - These young men and women were among the 1561 who were granted degrees Wednesday at the spring commencement of the University of Pittsburgh. They are, left to right:...John C. Hairston and Russell Anderson, both of whom finished their course in School of Medicine...-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh School of Medicine graduates John C. Hairston and Russell Anderson, posed in Cathedral of Learning
